            <p><a href="https://www.instituteforgovernment.org.uk/blog/rupert-mcneil-what-civil-service-tomorrow-will-look" target="_blank">Read this blog article</a> (external link)</p>

            <p>
                <a href="/prototypes/learner/v7/actions?action=addedToLearningPlan&type=blog">Add to learning plan</a>
